        <updateDate>2006-11-28T17:35:40Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[Homeowners' Emergency Mortgage Assistance Act - Directs the Secretary of Housing and Urban Development to establish a mortgage emergency assistance program for qualifying homeowners with National Housing Act-insured mortgages who are temporarily unable to meet their obligations due to financial hardship beyond their control. Requires homeowner repayment of such assistance and interest.]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
    <title>Homeowners' Emergency Mortgage Assistance Act</title>
